name: Just like what happens to dogs in the street
description: "Calm down my love" she said in my ear as if she was giving me an elephant pill. And then I slept. But now she was gone and everything felt like trains destroying the world, passing over me and my friends. Because chaos was dragging us all down. That was at some point what united us. I think that's what really brings people together; just like what happens to dogs in the street.
